casebody.data:
Stephen L. VOISINE and William E. Armstrong, III, petitioners,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 14-10154. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 11, 2016.

Motion of petitioners for appointment of counsel granted and Virginia G. Villa, Esq., of St. Croix Falls, Wisconsin, is appointed to serve as counsel for the petitioners in this case.
